Have I written custom code: NO

Exact command to reproduce: `bazel build -c opt //tensorflow/contrib/android:libtensorflow_inference.so \

   --host_crosstool_top=@bazel_tools//tools/cpp:toolchain \

I just know I don't build the `jar` file for Android.
